:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/msGetPropertyEnabled\"><code>msGetPropertyEnabled()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/msPutPropertyEnabled\"><code>msPutPropertyEnabled()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/removeProperty\"><code>removeProperty()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/setProperty\"><code>setProperty()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for CSSOM</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSS\"><code>CSS</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSConditionRule\"><code>CSSConditionRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSGroupingRule\"><code>CSSGroupingRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframeRule\"><code>CSSKeyframeRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframesRule\"><code>CSSKeyframesRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSMediaRule\"><code>CSSMediaRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNamespaceRule\"><code>CSSNamespaceRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSPageRule\"><code>CSSPageRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSRuleList\"><code>CSSRuleList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleRule\"><code>CSSStyleRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleSheet\"><code>CSSStyleSheet</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSSupportsRule\"><code>CSSSupportsRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CaretPosition\"><code>CaretPosition</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Screen\"><code>Screen</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet\"><code>StyleSheet</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StyleSheetList\"><code>StyleSheetList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TransitionEvent\"><code>TransitionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"概要","title":"概要","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>CSSStyleDeclaration</code> 表示了一個 CSS 屬性名值對（property-value pairs）的集合。它被用於幾個 API 當中：</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/style\"><code>HTMLElement.style</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> - to manipulate the style of a single element (&lt;elem style=\"...\"&gt;);</li>\n  <li>(TODO: reword) is an interface to the <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/1998/REC-CSS2-19980512/syndata.html#block\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">declaration block</a> returned by the <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/DOM/cssRule.style\"><code>style</code></a> property of a <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/DOM/cssRule\"><code>cssRule</code></a> in a <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/DOM/stylesheet\">stylesheet</a>, when the rule is a <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/DOM/cssRule#cssstylerule\">CSSStyleRule</a>.</li>\n  <li><code>CSSStyleDeclaration</code> is also a <strong>read-only</strong> interface to the result of <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/DOM/window.getComputedStyle\">window.getComputedStyle</a>().</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"屬性","title":"屬性","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"cssstyledeclaration.csstext_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/cssText\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration.cssText</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Textual representation of the declaration block. Setting this attribute changes the style.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"cssstyledeclaration.length_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/length\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration.length</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The number of properties. See the <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/item\"><code>item()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> method below.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"cssstyledeclaration.parentrule_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/parentRule\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration.parentRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The containing <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"方法","title":"方法","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"cssstyledeclaration.getpropertypriority_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/getPropertyPriority\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration.getPropertyPriority()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Returns the optional priority, \"important\".</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"cssstyledeclaration.getpropertyvalue_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/getPropertyValue\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration.getPropertyValue()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Returns the property value given a property name.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"cssstyledeclaration.item_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/item\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration.item()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Returns a property name.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"cssstyledeclaration.removeproperty_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/removeProperty\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration.removeProperty()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Removes a property from the CSS declaration block.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"cssstyledeclaration.setproperty_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/setProperty\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration.setProperty()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Modifies an existing CSS property or creates a new CSS property in the declaration block/.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"cssstyledeclaration.getpropertycssvalue_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/getPropertyCSSValue\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration.getPropertyCSSValue()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Only supported via getComputedStyle in Firefox. Returns the property value as a <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSPrimitiveValue\"><code>CSSPrimitiveValue</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> or <code>null</code> for <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/CSS/Shorthand_properties\">shorthand properties</a>.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"範例","title":"範例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> styleObj <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>styleSheets<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>cssRules<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>styleObj<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>cssText<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> styleObj<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">--</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> nameString <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> styleObj<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  styleObj<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">removeProperty</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>nameString<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>styleObj<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>cssText<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"備註","title":"備註","isH3":false,"content":"<p>The declaration block is that part of the style rule that appears within the braces and that actually provides the style definitions (for the selector, the part that comes before the braces).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"參見","title":"參見","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/Reference#index\">DOM CSS Properties</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"規範","id":"規範","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom/#the-cssstyledeclaration-interface","title":"CSS Object Model (CSSOM)"}],"query":"api.CSSStyleDeclaration"}}],"toc":[{"text":"概要","id":"概要"},{"text":"屬性","id":"屬性"},{"text":"方法","id":"方法"},{"text":"範例","id":"範例"},{"text":"備註","id":"備註"},{"text":"參見","id":"參見"},{"text":"規範","id":"規範"}],"summary":"CSSStyleDeclaration 表示了一個 CSS 屬性名值對（property-value pairs）的集合。它被用於幾個 API 當中：","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CSSStyleDeclaration","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"CSSStyleDeclaration","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"CSSStyleDeclaration","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"CSSStyleDeclaration","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"CSSStyleDeclaration","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"CSSStyleDeclaration","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/web/api/cssstyledeclaration","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/web/api/cssstyledeclaration/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web","title":"給開發者的網頁技術文件"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration","title":"CSSStyleDeclarat